Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. Put sweet potatoes in bowl of electric mixer and mash on medium speed. Add evaporated milk, eggs, SPLENDA(R) Brown Sugar Blend, and pumpkin pie spice. Beat until combined. Scrape filling into crust. Top with pecans. Bake 40 to 45 minutes, or until a tester inserted in center comes out clean. Cool completely on a wire rack.